Download "MielophoneDL.swf"  (Downloads-> Right-click -> Save as...)

Put the file in MIELOPHONE_DIR/extensions

Reset Mielophone

Enjoy it!

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage:

Download Button:            Current song is downloaded.
Download All Button:        All songs in PlayList are downloaded.
Mode Button:                Changes current download mode.

Download modes availables:	

N - Normal Mode:            AD to ~/Mielophone 
H - Hierarchy Mode:         AD to ~/Mielophone/Artist/Album/
A - Hierarchy A Mode:       AD to ~/Mielophone/Artist/
M - Manual Mode:            For each song, ask's destination folder.

(~ = User documents folder)
AD: Automatically downloaded.
---------------------------------------------------------------------